00:25:35,193 --> 00:25:36,746
Oh, my gosh!

513
00:25:36,747 --> 00:25:38,626
Hi, guys!

514
00:25:38,627 --> 00:25:43,082
Hi! Oh, um, Angie, you met Luke,

515
00:25:43,083 --> 00:25:44,381
and of course you recognize

516
00:25:44,382 --> 00:25:46,422
the beautiful Paulina Porizkova.

517
00:25:46,423 --> 00:25:47,623
She and I go way back.

518
00:25:47,624 --> 00:25:51,271
- How have you been? Give me a hug.
- Why?

519
00:25:52,112 --> 00:25:54,179
- What's wrong?
- You treated me like

520
