541
00:26:42,374 --> 00:26:45,957
No, sweetie, you were
the queen bitch diva...

542
00:26:45,958 --> 00:26:48,246
insulting photographers,
upsetting booking agents.

543
00:26:48,247 --> 00:26:50,465
