went down in flames.

544
00:26:50,466 --> 00:26:53,958
No. My career ended because
I decided to marry Carlos.

545
00:26:53,959 --> 00:26:56,370
You remember. I called
you the night he proposed.

546
00:26:56,371 --> 00:26:59,210
Yeah, and I told you
to grab that brass ring.

547
00:27:00,322 --> 00:27:02,434
Because I knew it was over for you,

548
00:27:03,328 --> 00:27:05,361
