552
00:27:26,414 --> 00:27:28,653
That one. But he's not here.

553
00:27:28,654 --> 00:27:32,106
Oh. Then I guess I'll just,
uh, leave these on his porch.

554
00:27:32,107 --> 00:27:33,661
If you want the dogs to eat it.

555
00:27:33,662 --> 00:27:35,815
Put it inside. It's unlocked.

556
00:28:16,255 --> 00:28:17,754
Mrs. Hodge?

557
00:28:20,462 --> 00:28:22,736
