you and Nick fighting...

734
00:38:56,297 --> 00:38:58,987
something about blowing your cover.

735
00:38:58,988 --> 00:39:01,626
Don't worry. I didn't
tell anybody. I just...

736
00:39:01,627 --> 00:39:04,658
I just want you to know that...

737
00:39:05,619 --> 00:39:09,227
