738
00:39:09,228 --> 00:39:12,129
and I know how lonely it can feel.

739
00:39:12,130 --> 00:39:16,011
So if you ever need a friend...

740
00:39:26,341 --> 00:39:28,863
Okay.

741
00:39:31,471 --> 00:39:35,180
